divs: sighting details on sept 8 2009 at 9:30 pm a friend and i were outside star gazing and playing with a new green laser. after being outside for about 15-20 minutes i saw a grey\black object in the sky. it was the size of a mini van and it did not have any shape the edges feathered into nothing,it was like a blotch in the sky. there were no lights and it blocked out the stars when it floated by. it was right above the trees so i would guess pretty accurately it was 150ft high or less and 75-100 ft away. there was no sound and that was very unnerving because of the size and how close it was. it was about a quarter mile from interstate 5. my neighbor that was with me saw it when i pointed it out using my green laser and that's where it got strange. when the laser hit the object it reflected off a rainbow of colors. there was enough light when it reflected colors to see a slight shape of what gave me the impression was the bottom. and that was it it went behind some trees. my neighbor just walked home without saying a thing. the whole thing took about 6 seconds.
Summary: Car sized grey mass floating above trees.
